==Old English==
===Etymology===
From Germanic ''*skeuban''.  Cognate with Old Frisian [[skuva|skūva]], Middle Low German [[schuven|schūven]] (Dutch [[schuiven]]), Old High German [[skioban]] (German [[schieben]]), Gothic [[𐌰𐍆𐍃𐌺𐌹𐌿𐌱𐌰𐌽]].

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/ˈʃuːvan/}}

